data.description: Are you looking for a home with lots of space in a sought after neighborhood? A neighborhood that is family friendly, complete with a pool, park, tennis courts, & stables nonetheless!! This home is on a corner lot with circular drive on over 3/4 acre. The main floor has spacious open concept living. The kitchen has a walk in pantry, ss appliances, farmhouse sink, granite counters & tons of storage. There is a sunroom that leads out to a large lot w/ beautiful flagstone firepit. Master suite & 2nd bedroom down. Upstairs has 2 huge bedrooms, flex room or could be 5th bedroom, & updated bath. Seller to provide $2K toward closing costs or carpet/paint w/ acceptable offer.
